quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,60,"Nende balia barusinjia ebia bahebwa emioyo chiabu nichiririre mbu toto balikalukha ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  23,61,"Abo nibo abanguyilanga amakhuwa amalayi, ne nibo bakaranjililanga."
  23,62,"Nafu shikhutukhanga omundu akaalanyala tawe, ne khuli nende eshitabu eshiboolanga katoto, nabo shibalikholelwa obubii tawe."
  23,63,"Halali emioyo chiabu chili mubukoyano nende ako, ne bali nende ebikhole biabakholanga ebilali ebio tawe (ebia Abandu abalayi bakholanga)."
  23,64,"Okhula shinga khwitsa okhutila (nende okhura mushinyasio) balia bali mubwokholo mubo, awo niwo wabalitsa okhulilikana."
  23,65,"“Mulalilikana inyangayino tawe, toto enywe shimulaona okhurulana ninafu tawe."
  23,66,"Toto mwasomelungwa tsinyaali tsianje, halali enywe mwakalukhanga inyuma khubisisilo bienyu."
  23,67,"Nimuyikholera obufuru, nimuyilomalomakhwo eshilo (khu Ikurani) nimulechele.""
  23,68,"Koo, shibaparangakhwo amakhuwa (akayetsa nako Omurumwa Muhammad), nohomba kabetsela akaletsela bapapa babu beyimbeli tawe?"
  23,69,"Nohomba shibamanya Omurumwa wabu tawe, kho nishichila bamuyingasinjia?"
  23,70,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu (Omurumwa uno) ni omulalu? Halali yabetsela khubwatoto, ne abaanji mubo obwatoto bwabasinya."
  23,71,"Ne obwatoto bulondanga obwikombi bwabu, likulu nende eshialo biakhabiyile nende ebilimwo bioosi. Halali khwabarerera ametsulisio kabu, halali bo beretsanga ehale nende ametsulisio kabu."
  23,72,"Nohomba obasabanga omurungo? Halali omurungo kwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nikwo omulayi, ne niye Omukabi omulayi muno umalayo."
  23,73,"Ne toto ewe obalanganga khunjila ingololofu."
  23,74,"Ne toto balia balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe, beretsanga ehale nende injila (ingololofu) eyo."